The release of the paper has been eagerly anticipated by investors and ratings agencies, who cite the financial and operational crisis at Eskom as one of the biggest risks to South Africa’s economy. JOHANNESBURG - Pravin Gordhan is on Tuesday releasing the Special Paper on Eskom, setting out in detail a comprehensive roadmap for the utility in a reformed electricity supply industry. The release of the paper has been eagerly anticipated by investors and ratings agencies, who cite the financial and operational crisis at Eskom as one of the biggest risks to South Africa’s economy. WATCH LIVE: Gordhan's Special Report on Eskom 